{"tid":1902200,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭月娥去信全體公務員：我深信各位會一如以往堅守崗位抗疫","createTime":"2020-02-28T08:22:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T13:08:07.000Z","uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"bee9350bff0b950e7abcae9fe73691c15a300340","tid":1902200,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T08:22:50.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥去信全體公務員，表示疫情前所未遇，深信公務員會一如以往齊心服務香港。她已要求官員及部門首長體諒同事處境，以體恤關懷的態度，回應同事問題，有需要時可向跨部門督導委員會暨指揮中心呈報及尋求直接指示。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥又說，公務員事務局局長及財經事務及庫務局局長會在今日發出聯合通函，回應公務員對口罩供應的關注。她表示鑑於疫情可能持續一段時間，政府會推行更多減少社交接觸的措施，並確保可為市民提供更多服務，強調調整策略不會影響抗疫目標。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bm09MQx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbm09MQx.jpg&h=470455e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1511428-20200228.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1511428-20200228.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=2%2B%2BG2pXT7lWIneVuf1o%2BJMwxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=54b0b556\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1511428-20200228.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=24b24d2c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1511428-20200228.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"086a8771a523e6ac590e3b9794e9a8821c9aaba1","tid":1902200,"uid":124410,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T08:23:54.000Z","msg":"可能知道自己時日無多<br />\n就落台了"},{"pid":"7c18ed259fa53a79720a647e6083f999c8708327","tid":1902200,"uid":212626,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T08:25:20.000Z","msg":"賤婦林奠又出恐嚇信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bec109bf8638e6ed44574bc08c928d2aa3e3f7d","tid":1902200,"uid":58630,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T08:26:56.000Z","msg":"手寫各位同事既意義係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.g